# This directory holds theme images
# Add the following files for the theme to display properly:
#
# hero-fallback.jpg        — 1920x1080 hero background
# hero-video.mp4           — Optional hero video
# welcome-fallback.jpg     — Welcome section image
# dest-bunaken.jpg         — Bunaken destination card
# dest-siladen.jpg         — Siladen destination card
# dest-bangka.jpg          — Bangka destination card
# dest-lembeh.jpg          — Lembeh destination card
# dest-default.jpg         — Fallback destination card
# boat-default.jpg         — Liveaboard card fallback
# boat-hero.jpg            — Single liveaboard hero fallback
# trip-default.jpg         — Trip card fallback
# hotel-default.jpg        — Hotel card fallback
# hotel-hero.jpg           — Single hotel hero fallback
# post-default.jpg         — Blog post hero fallback
# page-default.jpg         — Page hero fallback
# archive-default.jpg      — Archive hero fallback
# logo.png                 — Site logo (400x100)
# icon-192.png             — PWA icon 192x192
# icon-512.png             — PWA icon 512x512
# og-default.jpg           — Default Open Graph image (1200x630)
